ISLAMABAD, Jan 08 (APP):As many as three reports of Senate Standing Committee on Defence were presented in the Senate on Wednesday.
Chairman Standing Committee on Defence, Walid Iqbal presented all the three reports of the Committee including the bill further to amend the Pakistan Army Act, 1952 [The Pakistan Army (Amendment) Bill, 2020], the bill further to amend the Pakistan Air Force Act, 1953 [The Pakistan Air Force (Amendment) Bill, 2020] and the bill further to amend the Pakistan Navy Ordinance, 1961 [The Pakistan Navy (Amendment) Bill, 2020].
